Physiopedia Plus Ltd is committed to preserving the privacy of all users of our mobile applications. Please read the following privacy policy to understand how we use and protect the information that you provide to us.
By using a Physiopedia Plus Ltd mobile application (review the
Physiopedia Plus App terms of usage
), you consent to the collection, use and transfer of your information under the terms of this policy.
Information that we collect from you
As a user of the Physiopedia Plus App you are required to register an account on the
Plus website
. All data collected during this registration and through the use of this website is covered by the corresponding
privacy policy and terms of use
.
User-specific information such as your name, contact details, payment information or any other individually identifiable details are not collected or stored by our mobile applications.
When you use a Physiopedia Plus Ltd mobile application certain data related to this usage will be recorded anonymously to allow us to analyse and improve our services. All app use data is collected without user identifiable details and cannot be linked to you as an individual.
If you choose to contact us, we will retain information from messages you post to the website and e-mails or letters you send to us in order to respond to your requests.
Use of your information
We will use and analyse the information we collect so that we can administer, support, improve and develop our services.
Disclosure of your information
We may pass anonymised, aggregate information on the usage of our mobile applications to third parties but this will not include information that can be used to identify you.
For more details about this app see the
Physiopedia Plus App information
page.